'''Yang Water Horse also known as Ś£¨Śćą''' (mizu no euma, jinsui no uma, jingo) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|ŚĻ≤śĒĮ}}.

It is the 19th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Xinsi|ja|ŤĺõŚ∑≥}} and the following combination is {{ill|Guimi|ja|Áôłśú™}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and the Five Elements|ja|ťôįťôĹšļĒŤ°ĆśÄĚśÉ≥|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=ťôįťôĹšļĒŤ°Ć}}, the {{ill|Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|ŚćĀŚĻ≤}}‚Äô {{ill|Ren|ja|Ś£¨}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|śįī}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|ŚćĀšļĆśĒĮ}}‚Äô {{ill|Horse|ja|Śćą}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|ÁĀę}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Overcoming|ja|ÁõłŚČč}} (Water overcomes Fire).

== Years of Ren-Go ==
A {{ill|Common Era|ja|Ť•Ņśö¶}} year that leaves a remainder of 22 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|ŚĻī}} of Ren-Go.
