=== Events ===
* In {{ill|TenshŇć|ja|Ś§©ś≠£}} 10th Year (1582 AD) ‚Äď the {{ill|TenshŇć Ren-Go Rebellion|ja|Ś§©ś≠£Ś£¨Śćą„ĀģšĻĪ}}.
* In {{ill|Meiji|ja|śėéś≤Ľ}} 15th Year (1882 AD) ‚Äď the {{ill|Ren-Go Incident|ja|Ś£¨ŚćąšļčŚ§Č}} (also known as the Ren-Go Military Rebellion).

== Months of Ren-Go ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|Ť•Ņśö¶}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|ŚćĀŚĻ≤}} are {{ill|Geng|ja|Śļö}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|šĻô}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5śúą}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|śúą (śö¶)}} of Ren-Go. However, here the term ‚Äúmonth‚ÄĚ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Lunar Calendar|ja|śóßśö¶}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|ŤäíÁ®ģ}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|ŚįŹśöĎ}}) as applicable.

== Days of Ren-Go ==
The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|ťĀłśó•}} for a Ren-Go day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Ren-Go day is the 5th day of {{ill|Small Earth|ja|ÁäĮŚúü|lt=ShŇćdo|lt_ja=ŚįŹŚúü}}.

