It is the 19th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Xinsi|ja|ŤĺõŚ∑≥|1=Yin Metal Snake|2=ja|3=ŤĺõŚ∑≥|4=zh|5=ŤĺõŚ∑≥|6=ko|7=žč†žā¨ (ÍįĄžßÄ)|lt_ko=žč†žā¨|8=fr|9=Serpent de m√©tal|10=de|11=Metall-Schlange|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinsi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Metal Snake|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Guimi|ja|Áôłśú™|1=Yin Water Goat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guimi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Goat|qq=}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|ťôįťôĹšļĒŤ°ĆśÄĚśÉ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=ťôįťôĹšļĒŤ°Ć|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|ŚćĀŚĻ≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}‚Äô {{ill|Ren|ja|Ś£¨|1=Mizunoe (Ś£¨)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (Ś£¨)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|śįī|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|ŚćĀšļĆśĒĮ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}‚Äô {{ill|Horse|ja|Śćą|1=Horse (zodiac)|lt=Horse (Śćą)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|ÁĀę|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (ÁĀę)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Overcoming|ja|ÁõłŚČč|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Overcoming|qq=}} (Water overcomes Fire).

