ater (śįī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=–í–ĺ–ī–į (–£-—Ā—Ė–Ĺ)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische F√ľmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=ThŠĽßy (NgŇ© h√†nh)|10=pt|11=√Āgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (śįī)|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=–í–ĺ–ī–į (–£-—Ā—Ė–Ĺ)|lt=Water (śįī)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=–í–ĺ–ī–į (–£-—Ā—Ė–Ĺ)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische F√ľmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=ThŠĽßy (NgŇ© h√†nh)|10=pt|11=√Āgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (śįī)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (wuxing)|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|ŚćĀšļĆśĒĮ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}‚Äô {{ill|Horse|ja|Śćą|1=Horse (Zodiac)|lt=Horse (Śćą)|2=ja|3=Śćą|1=Horse (zodiac)|lt=Horse (Śćą)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse|13=User:Immanuelle/Horse (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|Fire (ÁĀę)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (ÁĀę)|2=uk|3=–í–ĺ–≥–ĺ–Ĺ—Ć (–£-—Ā—Ė–Ĺ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=HŠĽŹa (NgŇ© h√†nh)|10=ar|11=ōßŔĄŔÜōßōĪ (ŔąŔą ōīŔäŔÜōļ)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (ÁĀę)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire (wuxing)|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Overcoming|ja|ÁõłŚČč|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Overcoming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Overcoming|qq=}} (Water overcomes Fire).

