In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|Ť•Ņśö¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=Ť•Ņśö¶|4=zh|5=ŚÖ¨ŚÖÉ|6=es|7=Era com√ļn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|ŚćĀŚĻ≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Geng|ja|Śļö|1=Kanoe (Śļö)|lt=Kanoe (Śļö)|2=ja|3=Śļö|4=zh|5=Śļö|1=Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|šĻô|1=Kinoto (šĻô)|lt=Kinoto (šĻô)|2=ja|3=šĻô|4=zh|5=šĻô|1=Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5śúą|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May|qq=}} becomes the {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|śúą (śö¶)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (Calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (Calendar)|qq=}} of Ren-Go. However, here the term ‚Äúmonth‚ÄĚ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|śóßśö¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|ŤäíÁ®ģ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mangzhong|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mangzhong|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Xiaoshu|ja|ŚįŹśöĎ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaoshu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaoshu|qq=}}) as applicable.

