=== Events === * In [[:en:TenshŇć (Momoyama period)|TenshŇć Era]] 10th Year (1582 AD) ‚Äď the {{ill|TenshŇć Ren-Go Rebellion|ja|Ś§©ś≠£Ś£¨Śćą„ĀģšĻĪ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/TenshŇć Ren-Go Rebellion|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/TenshŇć Ren-Go Rebellion|qq=}}. * In [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 15th Year (1882 AD) ‚Äď the {{ill|Ren-Go Incident|ja|Ś£¨ŚćąšļčŚ§Č|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren-Go Incident|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren-Go Incident|qq=}} (also known as the Ren-Go Military Rebellion).
== Months of Ren-Go == In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Ten Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Geng|ja|Śļö|1=Kanoe (Śļö)|lt=Kanoe (Śļö)|2=ja|3=Śļö|4=zh|5=Śļö|1=Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (Śļö)|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|šĻô|1=Kinoto (šĻô)|lt=Kinoto (šĻô)|2=ja|3=šĻô|4=zh|5=šĻô|1=Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (šĻô)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:May|May]] becomes the [[:en:Month|Month (Calendar)]] of Ren-Go. However, here the term ‚Äúmonth‚ÄĚ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|śóßśö¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Mangzhong|Mangzhong]] until the day before [[:en:Xiaoshu|Xiaoshu]]) as applicable.
